*opencv-2.3.0 (18 Sep 2011)

  18 Sep 2011; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> +opencv-2.3.0.ebuild,
  +files/opencv-2.3.0-convert_sets_to_options.patch,
